==Documentation==
This template creates a full concept page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

The page structure follows the classic Giant Bomb wiki design:
* Hero section with image, title, and deck
* Tab navigation for sub-pages
* Two-column layout with wiki content on left and concept details sidebar on right

Concepts are wiki-wide topics that span multiple games, such as "Open World", "Boss Battle", 
"Microtransactions", or "Quick Time Events".

